Package: fireregimetools
Title: Tools for Summarizing Fire Regime Statistics From Simulations
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R:
    person(c("Alex", "M"), "Chubaty", , "achubaty@for-cast.ca", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-7146-8135"))
Description: Memory-bounded, Arrow-native summaries of simulated fire regimes.
    Per-replicate fire-size and annual-area-burned tables are written to
    partitioned parquet and reduced across replicates by pushing the aggregation
    down to Arrow compute (so the per-replicate rows are never all held in memory
    at once), plus a fire-size distribution plot. Companion to nrvtools for the
    fire side of natural-range-of-variation post-processing.
